 of the appreciation of $50,000 worth of Bitcoin. In general, if Bitcoin go=
es up, Non-Volcano has an advantage of $25,000. If Bitcoin goes down, Volca=
no returns $0 on the Bitcoin portion, while Non-Volcano returns something u=
